852844,"uid":22700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81dd29a6634f937dd1a67b8481ad9ac6739b968b","tid":1852844,"uid":125168,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"566cda8eb28e29f9e0898ef5fc299374962b1bd3","tid":1852844,"uid":161726,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"quote":{"pid":"5dbe9875d80f83afe9fc6a48523515c91ad50b59","tid":1852844,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T15:44:50.000Z","msg":"蓬佩奧形容中國共產黨是當今時代最大的威脅<br />\n21分鐘前 Share to Facebook<br />\n【Now新聞台】美國國務卿蓬佩奧形容，中國共產黨是當今時代中最大的威脅。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧和英國外相藍韜文在倫敦出席會議，討論國際安全局勢，以及跟中國的經濟關係。<br />\n<br />\n他表示國家主席習近平領導的共產黨，跟英國、美國的價值觀有很大出入，所以未來無論在世貿組織的架構，或者西方國家的基建和科技中，都要確保是按照民主原則治理。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧之後到唐寧街，拜會英國首相約翰遜。<br />\n<br />\n英國星期五會正式脫離歐盟，蓬佩奧表示，雖然美國不高興，英國讓內地電訊設備商華為有限度參與5G業務，但美國會同英國會強化雙方的特殊關係。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T15:47:28.000Z","msg":"睇清楚呀終國人<br />\n人地講個黨渣<br />\n唔係講你終國人呀<br />\n唔好對號入坐呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T15:49:42.000Z","msg":"佢之前都講過係針對中共，唔係中國人，識玩分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:12:49.000Z","msg":"但係依家既中國 黨國根本分唔開"},{"pid":"05fdd63991b98fe047ec7e5c64a824670a741440","tid":1852844,"uid":9956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:18:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />sir this way"},{"pid":"807ae27ad20cbe5a202bfbdcde7b88d415c41a0c","tid":1852844,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:24:04.000Z","msg":"皇天擊殺"},{"pid":"4435bc98ef379067726b9c5f5edeb2f115d62e12","tid":1852844,"uid":258106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79febbd5c90f5c11d74dc5719862b1d4b5b19467","tid":1852844,"uid":192776,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ba1f040e